1
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,960
Just go, bro.

2
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,440
We're hiring security guards here.

3
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,800
You've got a criminal record.

4
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,120
We really can't take you on.

5
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:03,960
Boss.

6
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,400
Please reconsider.

7
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,240
Just think about it.

8
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,400
Go on, go on, get going.

9
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,800
Boss, boss.

10
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:12,720
Where do you think you're going?

11
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:13,360
Don't run!

12
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:14,480
Have a sip, Sweetheart.

13
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,280
Don't touch me!

14
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,200
Don't go!

15
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,560
Running, huh?

16
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,760
"Don't touch me." Oh, getting shy?

17
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:19,800
Come play with me.

18
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,520
What are you mumbling about, Sweetheart?

19
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,240
Speak up!

20
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:24,000
Let us guys hear it.

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,000
Yeah, exactly.

22
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,040
Pretending to be Sadako?

23
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,680
Playing dress-up in the middle of the night?

24
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,360
Who the hell are you?

25
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,400
That's enough.

26
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,000
None of your business.

27
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,240
Help me!

28
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,560
You threw the first punch.

29
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,520
This is self-defense.

30
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,360
Go, go, hurry!

31
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,240
According to our nation's Criminal Law,

32
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,960
Article 237 stipulates that

33
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,240
using violence,

34
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,960
coercion, or any other means

35
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,840
to forcibly molest or insult women

36
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:25,160
is punishable by up to 5 years in prison.

37
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,760
Bro, I'm sorry!

38
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,960
Bro, which gang are you with?

39
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,760
Just a concerned citizen.

40
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,200
Okay?

41
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,080
Thanks for saving me yesterday.

42
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,600
If it weren't for you,

43
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,440
I wouldn't have known what to do.

44
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:48,840
Oh, right.

45
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,520
Does your head still hurt?

46
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,920
Have some of this calming tea I brewed.

47
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,600
Careful, it's hot.

48
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:59,520
A trial-stay isn't as scary as you think.

49
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,240
Maybe give it another thought?

50
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,720
I really can't do this job.

51
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,480
Why don't you talk to your boss?

52
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,560
I'll find another way to pay him back.

53
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,160
The boss already said,

54
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:12,000
if you ask that, the answer is no.

55
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,240
It's all written down here.

56
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,360
Your medical bills come to 2,580.

57
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,640
1,500 in compensation for the fight.

58
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,760
Clothes, 80.

59
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,360
Lodging fees total 50.

60
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,640
Minus your wages, you still owe the boss

61
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,200
exactly 3,800 yuan.

62
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,640
So until you've paid all of this back,

63
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:29,760
we can't return these belongings to you.

64
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,040
What are you doing?

65
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,960
Let me tell you,

66
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,480
I've got quite a temper.

67
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,000
If you guys don't want to be reasonable,

68
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,920
then I'll have to settle this another way.

69
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,240
Wait, wait!

70
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,600
Let's talk this out, okay?

71
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,840
Your birth chart is absolutely perfect.

72
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,240
You're a great fit for this line of work.

73
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,080
Plus, Daji hasn't hired anyone in ages.

74
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,400
Worst case, I'll go with you.

75
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,120
Even though

76
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,320
I won't be much help either.

77
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,480
Blood moon for eyes,

78
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,760
Dark wind for a throat,

79
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,640
Rotten earth molds the bones,

80
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:23,360
Corpse rain weaves the flesh,

81
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,040
This body is the curse,

82
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,000
This thought is the bind,

83
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:31,360
This hatred shall never end.

84
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,320
So you want a drink, huh?

85
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,800
One cup of wine, one life.

86
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:55,200
I doubt you'll live to walk out of here.

87
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,080
Such a tiny wound and you're done?

88
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,400
That tough, huh?

89
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,160
No wonder

90
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,720
your birth chart is so strong.

91
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,240
Think I'm being too nice?

92
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,320
Forgot who took you in?

93
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,520
Who?

94
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,360
Listen up.

95
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,680
The one who took you in is Xu Liuliu.

96
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,760
She's my best friend.

97
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,640
I'm Chen Shuyao.

98
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,760
If you dare bully Liuliu again,

99
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,160
I'll deal with you a whole different way.

100
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,240
I'm warning you.

101
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,360
Don't even think about running.

102
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:14,880
Hand it over.

103
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,600
I...

104
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,760
Oh, right.

105
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,680
You better not try anything funny.

106
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,360
Your ID card.

107
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,240
Liuliu's already got a photo of it.

108
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,240
If you dare run,

109
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:38,040
I'll call the cops and have you arrested.

110
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,640
I...

111
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,360
Oh, and...

112
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,040
Hey, big guy.

113
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,800
There's nothing around you.

114
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,480
Don't worry.

115
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,520
I guarantee it.

116
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,600
Hold onto this.

117
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,040
Mission accomplished.

118
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,280
The big guy's not bad.

119
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,120
Lin You, you're amazing!

120
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,600
Even Yaoyao is praising you.

121
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,680
Congrats on going full-time.

122
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,400
You got out and didn't even tell me?

123
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,200
Where are you right now?

124
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,360
I'll come pick you up.
